What? You got a shrink
ray back there?

17
00:00:52,825 --> 00:00:53,811
Yeah.

18
00:00:54,438 --> 00:00:56,862
Hey, remember that
time I said that thing

19
00:00:56,875 --> 00:00:59,732
about how do they fit a
pumpkin into that little cup?

20
00:00:59,746 --> 00:01:01,532
- Which time?
- The first time.

21
00:01:01,545 --> 00:01:04,491
Yeah. That was really funny.

22
00:01:04,645 --> 00:01:05,590
Right.

23
00:01:05,605 --> 00:01:07,533
All right, there's only two
reasons she'd laugh at that.

24
00:01:07,567 --> 00:01:09,973
