joke she's ever heard,

25
00:01:09,986 --> 00:01:12,911
or two, she likes you.
You should totally ask her out.

26
00:01:12,928 --> 00:01:13,521
You think?

27
00:01:13,536 --> 00:01:15,033
Yeah, that why you're not
back with Lily, right?

28
00:01:15,066 --> 00:01:17,510
So you can experience what
it's like to be single.

29
00:01:18,368 --> 00:01:19,990
Well, what if the heart
doesn't mean anything?

30
00:01:20,027 --> 00:01:22,001
What if she writes
it on all the cups?

31
00:01:22,018 --> 00:01:24,063
Mine says "Ted," no heart.

32
00:01:24,076 --> 00:01:27,092
Mine says... "Swarley."

33
00:01:27,956 --> 00:01:30,093
How'd they get
"Swarley" from "Barney"?

34
00:01:30,105 --> 00:01:31,190
It's not even a name.

35
00:01:31,207 --> 00:01:33,300
