called "Swarley"?

36
00:01:35,305 --> 00:01:38,243
Oh, please don't start
calling me "Swarley."

37
00:01:40,217 --> 00:01:42,661
This would never
happen at a bar!

38
00:01:44,558 --> 00:01:46,731
Man! What's up with Swarley?

39
00:01:46,746 --> 00:01:49,633
I know. You almost never see
old Swarlz get that upset.

40
00:02:06,256 --> 00:02:07,802
Hey, guess what?

41
00:02:07,815 --> 00:02:08,743
Oh, sorry.

42
00:02:08,755 --> 00:02:09,783
It's only my mom.

43
00:02:09,797 --> 00:02:11,933
She's just rambling
on like always.

44
00:02:12,428 --> 00:02:13,702
What happened?

45
00:02:13,715 --> 00:02:15,081
