I think I slept with you
because of that look.

67
00:03:13,145 --> 00:03:14,263
And it's fake?

68
00:03:14,275 --> 00:03:16,793
Oh, and you biting your lower lip,
shyly looking away

69
00:03:16,807 --> 00:03:19,330
