chest out is natural?

70
00:03:19,348 --> 00:03:21,012
Yeah, I hear you.

71
00:03:22,146 --> 00:03:23,720
- Hey!
- Hey, guys.

72
00:03:23,935 --> 00:03:25,741
Are you free tomorrow night?

73
