"help me catch the rat
in my apartment" party.

75
00:03:30,305 --> 00:03:32,990
That's a great idea.
You can put out cheese for both.

76
00:03:34,036 --> 00:03:35,883
I should invite
Marshall, right?

77
00:03:35,897 --> 00:03:37,223
It'd be weird if I didn't.

78
00:03:37,236 --> 00:03:39,290
Yeah, I don't think he can go.

79
00:03:39,318 --> 00:03:40,901
Really? Why not?

80
00:03:40,918 --> 00:03:43,242
Uh, okay, um...

81
00:03:43,298 --> 00:03:45,480
Lily, we have to
tell you something.

82
00:03:45,498 --> 00:03:47,363
Marshall has a date.

83
00:03:48,008 --> 00:03:50,780
Oh. Well... good for him.

84
00:03:50,798 --> 00:03:52,141
Really? You're okay with it?

85
00:03:52,158 --> 00:03:54,091
Look, we've been broken
up almost six months.

86
00:03:54,107 --> 00:03:56,333
