and told me what the look meant.

244
00:10:39,418 --> 00:10:41,263
If I pulled you aside,
I wouldn't need the look.

245
00:10:41,295 --> 00:10:42,523
Well, maybe if it was a
more distinctive look...

246
00:10:42,556 --> 00:10:44,391
Okay, the look isn't important.

247
00:10:44,406 --> 00:10:47,470
What's important is that
I can't stand the idea

248
00:10:47,486 --> 00:10:49,220
of Marshall dating
another woman.

249
00:10:49,236 --> 00:10:51,700
