he falls in love with her?

250
00:10:51,718 --> 00:10:53,493
Well, if it makes
you feel any better,

251
00:10:53,506 --> 00:10:56,050
Ted says she has
the crazy eyes.

252
00:10:56,067 --> 00:10:56,782
What's that?

253
00:10:56,797 --> 00:10:59,173
Apparently, a thing women
have that guys can see

254
00:10:59,186 --> 00:11:01,061
and it tells them that
the girl's crazy.

255
00:11:01,078 --> 00:11:03,752
Oh, kind of like how you
never want to date a guy

256
